{
	"nodes": [
		{
			"id": "g_main",
			"type": "group",
			"x": -50,
			"y": -50,
			"width": 3200,
			"height": 1800,
			"color": "3",
			"label": "Java完整学习路线图 (2025现代化)"
		},

		{
			"id": "n_title",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 0,
			"width": 600,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "# Java学习路线图 (2025)\n面向学生的现代化Java全栈学习路径"
		},

		{
			"id": "n_why_java",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 650,
			"y": 0,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## 为什么学Java？\n就业面广 · 生态成熟 · 薪资稳定 · 大厂首选 · Android开发 · 大数据生态"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_env",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 120,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 380,
			"color": "5",
			"label": "环境搭建与工具准备"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_env_jdk",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 20,
			"y": 160,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## JDK版本\n\n- **推荐 JDK 21** (LTS)\n- JDK 17 也可\n- OpenJDK 或 Oracle JDK\n- 了解 GraalVM 原生编译"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_env_ide",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 260,
			"y": 160,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## IDE选择\n\n- **IntelliJ IDEA** (首选)\n  - 社区版免费\n  - 学生免费旗舰版\n- VS Code (轻量)\n- Eclipse (备选)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_env_build",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 20,
			"y": 340,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 构建工具\n\n- Maven (传统稳定)\n- Gradle (现代主流)\n- 推荐先学 Maven"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_env_git",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 260,
			"y": 340,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 版本控制\n\n- Git 基础命令\n- GitHub / Gitee\n- 学会用 .gitignore"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_basic",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 540,
			"y": 120,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 380,
			"color": "6",
			"label": "第一阶段：Java基础 (4-6周)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_basic_syntax",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 560,
			"y": 160,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## 语法基础\n\n- 变量与数据类型\n- 运算符和表达式\n- 流程控制\n  - if/else/switch\n  - for/while/do-while\n- 数组 (一维/二维)\n- 方法定义和调用"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_basic_oop",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 800,
			"y": 160,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## 面向对象 (核心)\n\n- 类和对象\n- 封装/继承/多态\n- 抽象类和接口\n- 构造方法\n- static 和 final\n- this/super 关键字\n- toString/equals 重写"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_basic_api",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 560,
			"y": 380,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## 常用API\n\n- String / StringBuilder\n- Math / Random / Date\n- 包装类 (Integer等)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_basic_ex",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 800,
			"y": 380,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## 异常处理\n\n- try/catch/finally\n- throws/throw\n- 自定义异常"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_advanced",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 1080,
			"y": 120,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 380,
			"color": "2",
			"label": "第二阶段：Java进阶 (5-6周)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_adv_collections",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1100,
			"y": 160,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## 集合框架 (重点)\n\n- List (ArrayList/LinkedList)\n- Set (HashSet/TreeSet)\n- Map (HashMap/TreeMap)\n- Queue/Deque\n- Collections工具类\n- Iterator 迭代器"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_adv_generic",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1340,
			"y": 160,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## 泛型与高级特性\n\n- 泛型类/方法/接口\n- 泛型通配符\n- 枚举类型\n- 注解 (Annotation)\n- 反射 (Reflection)\n- Lambda 表达式"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_adv_io",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1100,
			"y": 380,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## IO与文件\n\n- 字节流/字符流\n- BufferedReader/Writer\n- NIO (Path/Files)\n- 序列化"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_adv_thread",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1340,
			"y": 380,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## 多线程基础\n\n- Thread / Runnable\n- synchronized\n- 线程池 (Executor)\n- CompletableFuture"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_modern",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 1620,
			"y": 120,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 380,
			"color": "1",
			"label": "第三阶段：现代Java特性 (2-3周)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_mod_stream",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1640,
			"y": 160,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## Stream API (重点)\n\n- filter / map / reduce\n- flatMap / collect\n- Optional 类\n- 并行流 parallelStream\n- Collectors 工具类\n- 链式编程思维"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_mod_features",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1880,
			"y": 160,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## Java 17-21 新特性\n\n- var 局部变量类型推断\n- Record 类 (不可变数据类)\n- Sealed 类 (密封类)\n- Text Block (多行字符串)\n- Pattern Matching\n- Switch 表达式\n- Virtual Threads (21)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_mod_func",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1640,
			"y": 380,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## 函数式编程\n\n- FunctionalInterface\n- 方法引用\n- Consumer/Supplier\n- Predicate/Function"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_mod_design",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1880,
			"y": 380,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## 设计模式入门\n\n- 单例模式\n- 工厂模式\n- 观察者模式\n- 策略模式"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_db",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 540,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 340,
			"color": "4",
			"label": "第四阶段：数据库 (3-4周)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_db_mysql",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 20,
			"y": 580,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## MySQL基础\n\n- SQL语法 (CRUD)\n- 表设计和约束\n- 索引原理\n- 事务 (ACID)\n- 联表查询\n- 子查询/视图"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_db_jdbc",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 260,
			"y": 580,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## JDBC\n\n- 驱动连接\n- Statement/PreparedStatement\n- ResultSet处理\n- 事务管理\n- 连接池 (Druid/HikariCP)\n- DAO模式"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_db_nosql",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 20,
			"y": 760,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## NoSQL (了解)\n\n- Redis 缓存\n- MongoDB 文档库\n- 使用场景对比"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_db_tool",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 260,
			"y": 760,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## 数据库工具\n\n- Navicat / DataGrip\n- DBeaver (免费)\n- SQL优化技巧"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_web",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 540,
			"y": 540,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 340,
			"color": "3",
			"label": "第五阶段：Web开发 (5-6周)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_web_basic",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 560,
			"y": 580,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## Web基础\n\n- HTTP协议原理\n- HTML/CSS/JS基础\n- Servlet/JSP (了解原理)\n- Tomcat 服务器\n- 请求/响应/会话\n- Cookie/Session"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_web_spring",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 800,
			"y": 580,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## Spring全家桶 (核心)\n\n- **Spring Boot 3** (必学)\n  - 自动配置原理\n  - Starter依赖管理\n- **Spring MVC**\n  - RESTful API\n  - 参数绑定\n- **Spring Security** (认证授权)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_web_mybatis",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 560,
			"y": 760,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## ORM框架\n\n- MyBatis / MyBatis-Plus\n- JPA / Hibernate\n- SQL映射和动态SQL"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_web_api",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 800,
			"y": 760,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## API开发\n\n- RESTful设计规范\n- Swagger/Knife4j文档\n- 统一响应封装\n- 全局异常处理"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_micro",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 1080,
			"y": 540,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 340,
			"color": "5",
			"label": "第六阶段：微服务与中间件 (4-6周)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_micro_svc",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1100,
			"y": 580,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 微服务架构\n\n- Spring Cloud\n- Nacos (注册/配置中心)\n- Gateway (网关路由)\n- OpenFeign (远程调用)\n- Sentinel (限流熔断)\n- 链路追踪 (SkyWalking)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_micro_mq",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1340,
			"y": 580,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 消息队列\n\n- RabbitMQ (入门首选)\n- Kafka (高吞吐)\n- RocketMQ (阿里系)\n- 异步解耦思想\n- 延迟队列/死信队列\n- 消息可靠性保证"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_micro_redis",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1100,
			"y": 760,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## Redis深入\n\n- 数据结构详解\n- 缓存穿透/击穿/雪崩\n- 分布式锁\n- Spring Data Redis"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_micro_search",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1340,
			"y": 760,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 搜索引擎\n\n- Elasticsearch\n- Kibana可视化\n- 分词与索引\n- 全文检索实践"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_frontend",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 1620,
			"y": 540,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 340,
			"color": "6",
			"label": "第七阶段：前端补充 (2-3周)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_fe_three",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1640,
			"y": 580,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## 三件套基础\n\n- **HTML5** 语义化标签\n- **CSS3** Flex/Grid布局\n- **JavaScript ES6+**\n  - 变量/函数/对象\n  - DOM操作\n  - fetch API\n- 不需要精通，够用即可"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_fe_vue",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1880,
			"y": 580,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## Vue 3 (推荐)\n\n- 组件化开发\n- 响应式数据\n- Vue Router\n- Pinia 状态管理\n- Axios 请求库\n- Element Plus UI"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_fe_ts",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1640,
			"y": 760,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## TypeScript (加分)\n\n- 类型系统\n- 接口/泛型\n- 与Java思维相通"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_fe_react",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1880,
			"y": 760,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## React (备选)\n\n- JSX语法\n- Hooks\n- 大厂偏好React\n- 学一个框架即可"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_deploy",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 920,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 300,
			"color": "2",
			"label": "第八阶段：部署与运维 (2-3周)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_deploy_linux",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 20,
			"y": 960,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## Linux基础\n\n- 常用命令 (cd/ls/grep等)\n- 文件权限管理\n- Vim编辑器\n- Shell脚本基础\n- 进程/服务管理\n- CentOS/Ubuntu"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_deploy_docker",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 260,
			"y": 960,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## Docker容器化\n\n- 镜像/容器概念\n- Dockerfile编写\n- Docker Compose\n- 常用镜像拉取\n- 容器网络和卷\n- Docker Hub"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_deploy_cicd",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 20,
			"y": 1140,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 40,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## CI/CD\n- Jenkins / GitHub Actions"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_deploy_cloud",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 260,
			"y": 1140,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 40,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## 云服务\n- 阿里云/腾讯云学生优惠"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_project",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 540,
			"y": 920,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 300,
			"color": "1",
			"label": "项目实战 (贯穿全程)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_proj_small",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 560,
			"y": 960,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## 入门项目\n\n1. 图书管理系统 (CRUD练手)\n2. 学生成绩管理系统\n3. 个人博客系统 (Spring Boot)\n4. 在线问卷调查系统"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_proj_mid",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 800,
			"y": 960,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## 进阶项目\n\n5. 电商系统 (前后端分离)\n6. 短信验证码登录系统\n7. 文件上传下载服务\n8. 在线聊天室 (WebSocket)"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_proj_big",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 560,
			"y": 1100,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## 毕设/竞赛项目\n\n9. 分布式秒杀系统\n10. 校园外卖平台\n11. 在线考试系统\n12. 智能推荐系统"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_proj_port",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 800,
			"y": 1100,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## 项目规范\n\n- Git分支管理\n- API文档编写\n- 单元测试 (JUnit5)\n- 代码评审习惯"
		},

		{
			"id": "g_interview",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 1080,
			"y": 920,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 300,
			"color": "3",
			"label": "面试与求职准备"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_interview_core",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1100,
			"y": 960,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## Java核心面试题\n\n- JVM内存模型\n- GC垃圾回收\n- HashMap底层原理\n- 并发与锁\n- Spring IOC/AOP\n- MyBatis缓存机制"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_interview_algo",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1340,
			"y": 960,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## 算法面试 (必备)\n\n- LeetCode Hot 100\n- 排序/二分/双指针\n- 链表/二叉树/回溯\n- 动态规划基础\n- 每天1-2题保持手感\n- 牛客网面经"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_interview_jvm",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1100,
			"y": 1100,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## JVM深入\n\n- 类加载机制\n- 内存区域 (堆/栈/方法区)\n- 垃圾回收算法\n- JVM调优参数\n- Arthas诊断工具"
		},
		{
			"id": "n_interview_soft",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1340,
			"y": 1100,
			"width": 220,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "3",
